---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Estudio F & A | Sucesiones, Familia y Laboral">
  
  <section id="inicio" class="relative bg-brand-dark text-white min-h-[90vh] md:min-h-screen flex items-center px-6 md:px-12 overflow-hidden pt-32 md:pt-40 pb-20 md:pb-24 border-b border-white/5">

    <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0 opacity-[0.03] bg-[url('https://www.transparenttextures.com/patterns/noise-pattern-with-subtle-cross-lines.png')]"></div>
    <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-[40rem] md:w-[60rem] h-[40rem] md:h-[60rem] bg-brand-primary/10 rounded-full blur-[100px] md:blur-[140px] pointer-events-none z-0 -translate-y-1/3 translate-x-1/3"></div>
    <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-[30rem] h-[30rem] bg-brand-primary/5 rounded-full blur-[100px] pointer-events-none z-0 translate-y-1/3 -translate-x-1/3"></div>

    <div class="container mx-auto max-w-6xl relative z-10 w-full flex flex-col items-start justify-center">

      <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-3 md:gap-4 mb-8 md:mb-10">
        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-brand-primary/10 border border-brand-primary/30 rounded-full px-4 py-2 backdrop-blur-md">
          <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-brand-primary animate-pulse shadow-[0_0_8px_#c59d5f]"></span>
          <span class="text-brand-primary font-body text-[9px] md:text-[10px] tracking-[0.2em] uppercase font-bold">
            Asesoría Legal Integral
          </span>
        </div>
        <a href="#testimonios" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-white/5 border border-white/10 rounded-full px-4 py-2 backdrop-blur-md hover:bg-white/10 hover:border-brand-primary/50 transition-colors cursor-pointer group">
          <div class="flex text-brand-primary text-[8px] md:text-[10px] tracking-[0.1em] group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform">★★★★★</div>
          <span class="text-white font-body text-[9px] md:text-[10px] tracking-[0.1em] uppercase font-bold">
            5.0 Google Reviews (38)
          </span>
        </a>
      </div>

      <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl md:text-6xl lg:text-7xl font-heading font-bold leading-[1.1] md:leading-[1.05] mb-8 text-white tracking-tight max-w-4xl relative z-10">
        La seriedad que <br />
        <span class="italic font-light text-brand-primary relative inline-block">
          tu caso exige.
          <svg class="absolute w-full h-3 md:h-4 -bottom-1 md:-bottom-2 left-0 text-brand-primary/40" viewBox="0 0 100 10" preserveAspectRatio="none">
            <path d="M0 5 Q 50 10 100 5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" />
          </svg>
        </span>
      </h1>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-8 lg:gap-12 w-full mt-2 md:mt-4">
        
        <div class="lg:col-span-6 relative">
          <div class="absolute left-0 top-2 w-1 h-full max-h-16 bg-gradient-to-b from-brand-primary to-transparent hidden md:block"></div>
          <p class="text-base md:text-xl font-light text-gray-300 leading-relaxed md:pl-6 max-w-xl relative z-10">
            Acompañamiento profesional y humano en momentos decisivos. Resolvemos conflictos de <span class="text-white font-medium">Sucesiones, Familia, Laboral y Tránsito</span> con total transparencia y rapidez.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="lg:col-span-6 flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center lg:justify-end gap-4 md:gap-6 w-full relative z-10">
          <a href="#contacto" class="relative group inline-flex items-center justify-center w-full sm:w-auto overflow-hidden bg-brand-primary px-8 py-5 md:px-10 md:py-6 font-body font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-[10px] md:text-[11px] text-brand-dark transition-all duration-500 shadow-[0_0_20px_rgba(197,157,95,0.2)] hover:shadow-[0_0_30px_rgba(197,157,95,0.4)] rounded-sm">
            <span class="absolute w-0 h-0 transition-all duration-500 ease-out bg-white rounded-full group-hover:w-72 group-hover:h-56"></span>
            <span class="relative flex items-center gap-3 group-hover:text-brand-dark">
              Consultar mi caso
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor" class="w-4 h-4 transform group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13.5 4.5L21 12m0 0l-7.5 7.5M21 12H3" /></svg>
            </span>
          </a>
          
          <a href="#areas" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-4 text-white hover:text-brand-primary transition-colors duration-300 font-body font-bold text-[10px] md:text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.2em] px-6 py-5 md:py-6 w-full sm:w-auto border border-white/20 hover:border-brand-primary/50 bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-sm group rounded-sm">
            Ver Especialidades
            <span class="w-0 h-px bg-brand-primary transition-all duration-300 group-hover:w-4 hidden sm:block"></span>
          </a>
        </div>

      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16 md:py-24 bg-brand-light px-6 relative z-10 border-b border-gray-200">
    <div class="container mx-auto max-w-6xl">
      
      <div class="text-center mb-12 md:mb-20">
        <span class="text-brand-primary font-body font-bold tracking-[0.3em] uppercase text-[10px] md:text-xs mb-3 md:mb-4 block">Entendemos tu situación</span>
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-heading font-bold text-brand-dark tracking-tight leading-[1.1]">
          ¿Necesitás resolver alguno <br class="md:hidden"/> de estos problemas?
        </h2>
        <p class="text-gray-500 font-light mt-4 md:mt-6 text-sm md:text-base max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
          Sabemos que iniciar un trámite legal puede generar incertidumbre. Nuestro objetivo es darte claridad desde el primer día.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 md:gap-8">
        
        <div class="bg-white p-8 md:p-10 relative group hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-500 border border-gray-100 hover:border-brand-primary/30 shadow-sm hover:shadow-[0_20px_40px_-15px_rgba(197,157,95,0.15)] overflow-hidden flex flex-col h-full rounded-sm">
          <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-1 h-0 bg-brand-primary transition-all duration-500 group-hover:h-full"></div>
          <div class="absolute -bottom-4 -right-4 text-[100px] md:text-[130px] font-heading font-bold text-gray-50 group-hover:text-brand-primary/5 transition-colors duration-500 pointer-events-none select-none leading-none">01</div>
          
          <div class="relative z-10 flex-grow">
            <span class="text-[9px] md:text-[10px] font-body tracking-[0.2em] uppercase text-brand-primary font-bold mb-4 block">Sucesiones</span>
            <h3 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-heading font-bold text-brand-dark mb-4 leading-tight">
              "Necesito destrabar <br/> el patrimonio familiar"
            </h3>
            <p class="font-light text-gray-500 text-sm md:text-base leading-relaxed">
              Iniciamos el proceso sucesorio de manera ágil para que puedas disponer, vender o dividir los bienes inmuebles o cuentas bancarias correspondientes.
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="mt-8 pt-6 border-t border-gray-100 relative z-10">
            <a href="#contacto" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-[10px] md:text-xs font-body font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-brand-dark group-hover:text-brand-primary transition-colors">
              Iniciar Trámite <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor" class="w-4 h-4 transform group-hover:translate-x-1.5 transition-transform duration-300"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13.5 4.5L21 12m0 0l-7.5 7.5M21 12H3" /></svg>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white p-8 md:p-10 relative group hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-500 border border-gray-100 hover:border-brand-primary/30 shadow-sm hover:shadow-[0_20px_40px_-15px_rgba(197,157,95,0.15)] overflow-hidden flex flex-col h-full rounded-sm">
          <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-1 h-0 bg-brand-primary transition-all duration-500 group-hover:h-full"></div>
          <div class="absolute -bottom-4 -right-4 text-[100px] md:text-[130px] font-heading font-bold text-gray-50 group-hover:text-brand-primary/5 transition-colors duration-500 pointer-events-none select-none leading-none">02</div>
          
          <div class="relative z-10 flex-grow">
            <span class="text-[9px] md:text-[10px] font-body tracking-[0.2em] uppercase text-brand-primary font-bold mb-4 block">Derecho de Familia</span>
            <h3 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-heading font-bold text-brand-dark mb-4 leading-tight">
              "Busco organizarme <br/> legalmente tras separarme"
            </h3>
            <p class="font-light text-gray-500 text-sm md:text-base leading-relaxed">
              Te acompañamos en procesos de divorcio, acuerdos de alimentos y régimen de comunicación, priorizando siempre la resolución pacífica de los conflictos.
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="mt-8 pt-6 border-t border-gray-100 relative z-10">
            <a href="#contacto" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-[10px] md:text-xs font-body font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-brand-dark group-hover:text-brand-primary transition-colors">
              Consultar Familia <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor" class="w-4 h-4 transform group-hover:translate-x-1.5 transition-transform duration-300"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13.5 4.5L21 12m0 0l-7.5 7.5M21 12H3" /></svg>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white p-8 md:p-10 relative group hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-500 border border-gray-100 hover:border-brand-primary/30 shadow-sm hover:shadow-[0_20px_40px_-15px_rgba(197,157,95,0.15)] overflow-hidden flex flex-col h-full rounded-sm">
          <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-1 h-0 bg-brand-primary transition-all duration-500 group-hover:h-full"></div>
          <div class="absolute -bottom-4 -right-4 text-[100px] md:text-[130px] font-heading font-bold text-gray-50 group-hover:text-brand-primary/5 transition-colors duration-500 pointer-events-none select-none leading-none">03</div>
          
          <div class="relative z-10 flex-grow">
            <span class="text-[9px] md:text-[10px] font-body tracking-[0.2em] uppercase text-brand-primary font-bold mb-4 block">Derecho Laboral</span>
            <h3 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-heading font-bold text-brand-dark mb-4 leading-tight">
              "Me despidieron o <br/> trabajo sin registrar"
            </h3>
            <p class="font-light text-gray-500 text-sm md:text-base leading-relaxed">
              Exigimos tu correcta indemnización frente a despidos sin causa, trabajo "en negro" o diferencias salariales. No permitas que vulneren tus derechos como trabajador.
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="mt-8 pt-6 border-t border-gray-100 relative z-10">
            <a href="#contacto" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-[10px] md:text-xs font-body font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-brand-dark group-hover:text-brand-primary transition-colors">
              Hacer reclamo <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor" class="w-4 h-4 transform group-hover:translate-x-1.5 transition-transform duration-300"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13.5 4.5L21 12m0 0l-7.5 7.5M21 12H3" /></svg>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="areas" class="py-20 md:py-32 bg-white px-6 relative z-10">
    <div class="container mx-auto max-w-6xl">
      
      <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-start md:items-end mb-12 md:mb-20 gap-6 md:gap-8">
        <div>
          <span class="text-brand-primary font-body font-bold tracking-[0.3em] uppercase text-[10px] md:text-xs mb-3 md:mb-4 block">Práctica Legal</span>
          <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-heading font-bold text-brand-dark tracking-tight leading-[1.1]">Dominio en cada área.</h2>
        </div>
        <p class="text-base md:text-lg text-gray-500 font-light leading-relaxed md:leading-loose max-w-sm md:text-right border-l-2 md:border-l-0 md:border-r-2 border-brand-primary pl-4 md:pl-0 md:pr-4">
          Defendemos tus intereses con la máxima exigencia técnica y un trato personalizado continuo.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6 md:gap-8">
        
        <div class="lg:col-span-2 relative bg-brand-dark p-8 md:p-12 border border-white/10 overflow-hidden group transition-all duration-500 hover:-translate-y-1 shadow-2xl shadow-brand-dark/20 rounded-sm">
          <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-64 h-64 bg-brand-primary/20 rounded-full blur-[80px] pointer-events-none group-hover:bg-brand-primary/30 transition-colors duration-500"></div>
          <div class="absolute -bottom-6 -right-2 text-[100px] md:text-[140px] font-heading font-bold text-white/5 group-hover:text-brand-primary/10 transition-colors duration-500 pointer-events-none select-none leading-none">01</div>
          
          <div class="relative z-10 flex flex-col h-full">
            <div>
              <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 mb-4">
                <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-brand-primary animate-pulse"></span>
                <span class="text-[10px] md:text-[11px] font-body font-bold text-white uppercase tracking-widest block">Trámite Ágil</span>
              </div>
              
              <h3 class="text-2xl md:text-4xl font-heading font-bold text-white mb-6 leading-tight">Sucesiones <br/> y Declaratorias</h3>
              
              <ul class="space-y-4 text-sm md:text-base font-medium text-gray-300 mb-10">
                <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                  <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor" class="w-4 h-4 md:w-5 md:h-5 text-brand-primary shrink-0"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.403 12.652a3 3 0 000-5.304 3 3 0 00-3.75-3.751 3 3 0 00-5.305 0 3 3 0 00-3.751 3.75 3 3 0 000 5.305 3 3 0 003.75 3.751 3 3 0 005.305 0 3 3 0 003.751-3.75zm-2.546-4.46a.75.75 0 00-1.214-.883l-3.483 4.79-1.88-1.88a.75.75 0 10-1.06 1.061l2.5 2.5a.75.75 0 001.137-.089l4-5.5z" clip-rule="evenodd" /></svg>
                  <span class="text-white font-bold tracking-wide">Resolución de expedientes en tiempo récord</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                  <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor" class="w-4 h-4 md:w-5 md:h-5 text-brand-primary shrink-0"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.403 12.652a3 3 0 000-5.304 3 3 0 00-3.75-3.751 3 3 0 00-5.305 0 3 3 0 00-3.751 3.75 3 3 0 000 5.305 3 3 0 003.75 3.751 3 3 0 005.305 0 3 3 0 003.751-3.75zm-2.546-4.46a.75.75 0 00-1.214-.883l-3.483 4.79-1.88-1.88a.75.75 0 10-1.06 1.061l2.5 2.5a.75.75 0 001.137-.089l4-5.5z" clip-rule="evenodd" /></svg>
                  <span>Inscripción de propiedades y vehículos</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                  <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor" class="w-4 h-4 md:w-5 md:h-5 text-brand-primary shrink-0"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.403 12.652a3 3 0 000-5.304 3 3 0 00-3.75-3.751 3 3 0 00-5.305 0 3 3 0 00-3.751 3.75 3 3 0 000 5.305 3 3 0 003.75 3.751 3 3 0 005.305 0 3 3 0 003.751-3.75zm-2.546-4.46a.75.75 0 00-1.214-.883l-3.483 4.79-1.88-1.88a.75.75 0 10-1.06 1.061l2.5 2.5a.75.75 0 001.137-.089l4-5.5z" clip-rule="evenodd" /></svg>
                  <span>Protección del patrimonio contra terceros</span>
                </li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="mt-auto pt-6 border-t border-white/10">
              <a href="#contacto" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-[10px] md:text-xs font-body font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-brand-primary group-hover:text-white transition-colors">
                Trámites sucesorios <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor" class="w-4 h-4 transform group-hover:translate-x-1.5 transition-transform duration-300"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13.5 4.5L21 12m0 0l-7.5 7.5M21 12H3" /></svg>
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="relative bg-brand-light p-8 md:p-10 border border-gray-200 overflow-hidden group transition-all duration-500 hover:shadow-[0_20px_40px_-15px_rgba(0,0,0,0.05)] hover:-translate-y-1 rounded-sm">
          <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-0 h-1 bg-brand-primary transition-all duration-500 group-hover:w-full"></div>
          <div class="absolute -bottom-6 -right-2 text-[100px] md:text-[140px] font-heading font-bold text-gray-200 group-hover:text-brand-primary/10 transition-colors duration-500 pointer-events-none select-none leading-none">02</div>
          <div class="relative z-10 flex flex-col h-full">
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-heading font-bold text-brand-dark mb-6 leading-tight">Familia <br/> y Divorcios</h3>
              <ul class="space-y-4 text-sm md:text-base font-medium text-gray-600 mb-10">
                <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                  <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor" class="w-4 h-4 md:w-5 md:h-5 text-brand-primary shrink-0"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.403 12.652a3 3 0 000-5.304 3 3 0 00-3.75-3.751 3 3 0 00-5.305 0 3 3 0 00-3.751 3.75 3 3 0 000 5.305 3 3 0 003.75 3.751 3 3 0 005.305 0 3 3 0 003.751-3.75zm-2.546-4.46a.75.75 0 00-1.214-.883l-3.483 4.79-1.88-1.88a.75.75 0 10-1.06 1.061l2.5 2.5a.75.75 0 001.137-.089l4-5.5z" clip-rule="evenodd" /></svg>
                  <span>Divorcios Express / Contradictorios</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                  <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor" class="w-4 h-4 md:w-5 md:h-5 text-brand-primary shrink-0"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.403 12.652a3 3 0 000-5.304 3 3 0 00-3.75-3.751 3 3 0 00-5.305 0 3 3 0 00-3.751 3.75 3 3 0 000 5.305 3 3 0 003.75 3.751 3 3 0 005.305 0 3 3 0 003.751-3.75zm-2.546-4.46a.75.75 0 00-1.214-.883l-3.483 4.79-1.88-1.88a.75.75 0 10-1.06 1.061l2.5 2.5a.75.75 0 001.137-.089l4-5.5z" clip-rule="evenodd" /></svg>
                  <span>Acuerdos de Alimentos y Régimen</span>
                </li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="mt-auto pt-6 border-t border-gray-200">
              <a href="#contacto" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-[10px] md:text-xs font-body font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-brand-dark group-hover:text-brand-primary transition-colors">
                Consultar Familia <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor" class="w-4 h-4 transform group-hover:translate-x-1.5 transition-transform duration-300"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13.5 4.5L21 12m0 0l-7.5 7.5M21 12H3" /></svg>
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="relative bg-brand-light p-8 md:p-10 border border-gray-200 overflow-hidden group transition-all duration-500 hover:shadow-[0_20px_40px_-15px_rgba(0,0,0,0.05)] hover:-translate-y-1 lg:col-start-2 lg:col-end-4 lg:row-start-2 rounded-sm">
          <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-0 h-1 bg-brand-primary transition-all duration-500 group-hover:w-full"></div>
          <div class="absolute -bottom-6 -right-2 text-[100px] md:text-[140px] font-heading font-bold text-gray-200 group-hover:text-brand-primary/10 transition-colors duration-500 pointer-events-none select-none leading-none">03</div>
          <div class="relative z-10 flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-6 md:gap-12 h-full">
            <div class="w-full md:w-1/2">
              <h3 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-heading font-bold text-brand-dark mb-4 leading-tight">Laboral <br/> y Tránsito</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm md:text-base font-light mb-6">No aceptes menos. Reclamamos frente a empresas, ARTs y Aseguradoras.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 flex flex-col">
              <ul class="space-y-4 text-sm md:text-base font-medium text-gray-600 mb-10">
                <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                  <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor" class="w-4 h-4 md:w-5 md:h-5 text-brand-primary shrink-0"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.403 12.652a3 3 0 000-5.304 3 3 0 00-3.75-3.751 3 3 0 00-5.305 0 3 3 0 00-3.751 3.75 3 3 0 000 5.305 3 3 0 003.75 3.751 3 3 0 005.305 0 3 3 0 003.751-3.75zm-2.546-4.46a.75.75 0 00-1.214-.883l-3.483 4.79-1.88-1.88a.75.75 0 10-1.06 1.061l2.5 2.5a.75.75 0 001.137-.089l4-5.5z" clip-rule="evenodd" /></svg>
                  <span>Indemnizaciones por despidos</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                  <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor" class="w-4 h-4 md:w-5 md:h-5 text-brand-primary shrink-0"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.403 12.652a3 3 0 000-5.304 3 3 0 00-3.75-3.751 3 3 0 00-5.305 0 3 3 0 00-3.751 3.75 3 3 0 000 5.305 3 3 0 003.75 3.751 3 3 0 005.305 0 3 3 0 003.751-3.75zm-2.546-4.46a.75.75 0 00-1.214-.883l-3.483 4.79-1.88-1.88a.75.75 0 10-1.06 1.061l2.5 2.5a.75.75 0 001.137-.089l4-5.5z" clip-rule="evenodd" /></svg>
                  <span>Choques y Reclamos por Lesiones</span>
                </li>
              </ul>
              <div class="mt-auto pt-6 border-t border-gray-200">
